{"id":152629,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/拒绝造成痛苦/","date":"2011-05-16T19:00:32Z","modified":"2011-05-17T00:27:43Z","title":"&#8220;拒绝造成痛苦&#8221;","content":"<p>一项新研究发现，社交拒绝不仅仅是让被拒绝者心情变糟，它能真正产生痛苦。 研究人员招募了刚刚遭遇分手剧变的志愿者，请他们观看前爱人的照片，回忆让人痛不欲生的拒绝经历。期间用功能性核磁共振成像（fMRI）监控志愿者的大脑活动。然后是实验中非常有意思的部分，志愿者的左前臂遭遇了两次热刺激，第一次是伤害性热刺激，模拟热咖啡溅洒在身上；第二次是非伤害性热刺激。fMRI的监控结果显示，分手和热咖啡溅洒在大脑中产生了类似的活动。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/14defdbb/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E6%8B%92%E7%BB%9D%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E7%97%9B%E8%8B%A6&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fscience.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F16%2F0717200%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E6%8B%92%E7%BB%9D%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E7%97%9B%E8%8B%A6&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fscience.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F16%2F0717200%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101092551024/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14defdbb/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101092551024/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/14defdbb/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=XiDONh-1OL4:MAocRLBDgPo:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=XiDONh-1OL4:MAocRLBDgPo:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时